headline: Fiserv Small Business Index® for December 2024: Retail and Services Lead as Small Business Finishes on Upswing
summary: MILWAUKEE, January 06, 2025--Fiserv, Inc. (NYSE: FI), a leading global provider of payments and financial services technology, has published the Fiserv Small Business Index for December 2024. Nationally, the seasonally adjusted Index for December was 146, a three-point increase from November. This continued growth is a positive sign for small business owners, many of which saw December cap off a strong holiday season.
